[Swithin Swaray](https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=663490015) went
further on Facebook, giving his opinion of some weak points of the Ghana team:

> The Black Star has not got what it takes to win CAN2012….30 years down the
> line, we are still counting. Lacking ideas up front, no fire power, no man
> daring enough to shoot from around the 18.

Ghana and Mali each got the better of their respective opponents after long
matches of more than 120 minutes. Will they have the necessary energy and
stamina to face Zambia and the Côte d'Ivoire?

The semi-finals of Wednesday 8 February will reveal the answer.

